    "We next examine techniques aimed at mitigating such bias, and assess the extent of label bias remaining after their application.",
    "We report our results for Llama-2 models in Fig. 3, and observe similar trends for other models (App.",
    "We first consider the effect of bias mitigation on model performance (Fig. 3a) using the three methods described in §3.3: contextual calibration (CC), domain-context calibration (DC), and fewshot fine-tuning with LoRA.",
